## Phase 0: Requirement Understanding

### Default primary entry (read first)

This workflow is the **default primary entry** for most tasks. When the requirement is slightly ambiguous, ask for clarification **once** (and only do minimal context reads if needed), then continue planning. Suggest `/harness-vision` only when the user explicitly wants long-horizon exploration, standing roadmap/backlog governance, or vision-first multi-round framing — not as a mandatory interrupt mid-session.

Read the user's requirement. If ambiguous, ask for clarification **once** —
then proceed with best interpretation.

